---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About | Frédéric - Independent AI Automation Expert"
  description="Meet Frédéric, your dedicated AI automation expert. Direct consultation, competitive pricing, and personalized solutions. No agency overhead, just expert-level automation delivered in 72 hours."
  keywords="AI expert, freelance automation consultant, Frédéric, independent AI developer, business automation expert, AI consultant, direct hire expert">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-32">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">
        AI Automation Expert
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-300">
        I'm Frédéric, an independent expert specializing in AI integration and business process automation. I work directly with you to transform your ideas into concrete solutions, without intermediaries or structural overhead costs.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">My Mission</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-300">
            Making AI and automation accessible to businesses of all sizes. I design robust, scalable data pipelines that connect your systems, unlock your data's potential, and enable your teams to focus on what matters most: innovation and growth.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">My Approach</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-300">
            Since 2023, I've been helping businesses through their digital transformation. My direct and personalized approach offers flexibility and responsiveness that large firms can't match, with pricing tailored to your budget.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24">
      <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white text-center mb-8">Why Work With an Independent Expert?</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">Direct Contact</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-1">You work directly with the technical expert, no middlemen</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">Competitive Pricing</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-1">No overhead costs, you only pay for expertise</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">Maximum Flexibility</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-1">Quick adaptation to your needs without bureaucracy</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">Personal Commitment</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-300 text-sm mt-1">Your success is my priority and my reputation depends on it</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <img class="mx-auto h-32 w-32 rounded-full object-cover mb-6" src="/images/frederic-profile.png" alt="Frédéric, AI & Automation Expert" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">Frédéric</h2>
        <p class="text-indigo-400 text-lg mt-2">AI & Automation Expert</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-neutral-300">
          With extensive experience in AI solution development and integration, I help businesses through their digital transformation. My expertise covers the entire value chain: from analyzing your needs to deploying custom solutions in production.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-neutral-400">
          For projects requiring specific skills, I collaborate with a carefully selected network of partners, while remaining your single point of contact.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout> 